# AICOE Public Page -- Implementation Plan

**Project**: 45-aicoe-page
**Phase 1**: Migration baseline -- COMPLETE 2026-02-22
**Phase 2**: EVA team alignment -- COMPLETE 2026-02-24 22:38 ET
**Phase 3**: Content pages + CI -- COMPLETE 2026-02-24

---

## Feature: EVA Team Structural Alignment [ID=F45-01]

Bring 45-aicoe-page to the same structural standard as 44-eva-jp-spark.

### Story: Replace FluentProvider with GCThemeProvider [ID=F45-01-001]
Remove bare FluentProvider + webLightTheme. Wrap app with GCThemeProvider from @eva/gc-design-system.

### Story: Add AnnouncerProvider for WCAG aria-live [ID=F45-01-002]
Implement AnnouncerProvider and useAnnouncer hook so route changes are announced to screen readers.

### Story: Add HashRouter and React.StrictMode [ID=F45-01-003]
Wrap entry with HashRouter and React.StrictMode to match 44-eva-jp-spark bootstrap pattern.

### Story: Wire @eva shared deps [ID=F45-01-004]
Add file: references to 31-eva-faces shared packages. Add .npmrc with install-links + legacy-peer-deps for Windows.

### Story: Remove @github/spark Vite plugin [ID=F45-01-005]
Remove sparkPlugin from vite.config.ts and @github/spark from package.json.

---

## Feature: Bilingual i18n Scaffold [ID=F45-02]

### Story: Add i18next with LanguageDetector [ID=F45-02-001]
Create src/i18n/i18n.tsx: i18next + browser-languagedetector + react-i18next. Detect from localStorage then navigator. Sync document.documentElement.lang on change.

### Story: Seed EN and FR locale files [ID=F45-02-002]
Create src/i18n/locales/en/resources_en.json and fr/resources_fr.json with all UI keys.

---

## Feature: Layout Shell [ID=F45-03]

### Story: Build Layout component with skip-link and nav [ID=F45-03-001]
Create src/pages/layout/Layout.tsx with skip-to-main link, brand header, bilingual nav, language toggle, main outlet, footer.

### Story: Wire route-change announcer effect [ID=F45-03-002]
In Layout.tsx, useEffect on location.pathname: call announce(document.title) and focus mainContent h2 after 150ms.

---

